HEADWORD: Rostrifera
<hw>Ros*trif"e*ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL.,
fr. L. <ets>rostrum</ets> beak + <ets>ferre</ets> to bear.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A division of pectinibranchiate gastropods,
having the head prolonged into a snout which is not
retractile.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

